<% content_for :main_content do %>

<div class="container mx-auto mt-8 mb-5">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-4">About Us</h1>
    <p class="text-lg mb-4">Welcome to the Confessions Website, where users can freely express their thoughts and feelings anonymously.</p>

    <!-- Features section -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
        <div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Confess Anything</h2>
            <p>Users can share their confessions anonymously, expressing anything on their minds without fear of judgment.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Categorize Confessions</h2>
            <p>Confessions can be categorized into various topics or themes, allowing users to browse and filter confessions based on their interests.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Like/Dislike Confessions</h2>
            <p>Users can react to confessions by liking or disliking them, providing feedback and showing support for the confessions they resonate with.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Commenting System</h2>
            <p>Each confession can be commented on, allowing users to engage in discussions, offer support, or share their perspectives with others.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="p-4 bg-white shadow rounded-md">
            <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Confession Challenges</h2>
            <p>Users can participate in confession challenges, where they can compete or collaborate with others to share confessions based on specific themes or prompts.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<%end%>